gw.plugin.billing

Interface PaymentPlanData

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    InstallmentPlanData, ReportingPlanData

    public interface PaymentPlanData
    Defines behaviors supported by non-persisted PaymentPlanData types.

      • isSameBillingPaymentPlan

        boolean isSameBillingPaymentPlan(PaymentPlanSummary summary)
        Determines whether the passed-in PaymentPlanSummary and this PaymentPlanData object both refer to the same Payment Plan in the billing system. Returns true if so, false otherwise, or if summary is null.
        Parameters:
        summary - the PaymentPlanSummary bean to compare to this PaymentPlanData object
        Returns:
        true if summary and this object both refer to the same billing system payment plan, false otherwise, or if summary is null.

      • isSameBillingPaymentPlan

        Parameters:
        otherPlan - the PaymentPlanData to compare to this PaymentPlanData object
        Returns:
        true if otherPlan and this object both refer to the same billing system payment plan, false otherwise, or if otherPlan is null.
